791
00:40:17,300 --> 00:40:19,300
 puno pomagati.

792
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:25,300
 na sredstvo koje može biti iskoristeno na veće dobro drugoga,

793
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:30,300
